The paper discusses a library that provides a record-oriented data store with schema management, query and indexing facilities, and multi-tenancy support. These topics are closely related to database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the use of the library in CloudKit, which is a cloud backend service, indicating a potential connection to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the extensibility of the library, which could be relevant to programming languages (cs.PL).
